Package org.sakaiproject.entitybroker.providers

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EntityPropertiesService
    This provides the entity system with a way to access properties (and then exposes this to others via the developer helper service)
    EntityRequestHandler
    Handles the URL/request processing for an entity in a central location
    EntityRESTProvider
    Handles anything REST based that is not part of the core EB registration piece
    ExternalIntegrationProvider  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MembershipEntityProvider
    This provides access to memberships as entities
    MembershipEntityProvider.SiteGroup
    This contains the site and optionally group for a given reference
    ServerConfigEntityProvider
    This provides access to the server configuration as entities, output access only though, no setting of configuration
    ServerConfigEntityProvider.ESCComparator  
    SessionEntityProvider
    Entity provider for Sakai Sessions
    SiteEntityProvider
    Creates a provider for dealing with sites
    UserEntityProvider
    Entity Provider for users
